{"tid":2331634,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"后翼棄兵 呢段劇情真係好感人","createTime":"2020-12-19T03:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T04:08:06.000Z","uid":61443,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a6f509f6336a1dff5a0fd267561f304abb486b","tid":2331634,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:15:12.000Z","msg":"師父死嗰陣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚴格嚟講唔係佢師傅 <br />\n因為女主轉過頭已經勁過佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最感人嘅位係<br />\n到死嗰陣師傅一路都冇揾過女主<br />\n呢個位做得好好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為人地出咗名就去揾返人<br />\n會比人覺得沾佢光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女主返到孤兒院<br />\n見到剪布板嗰幕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要見到當初問佢借錢封信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母死冇喊<br />\n後母死都冇喊<br />\n師傅死咗女主真係喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩最後女主<br />\n同記者介紹返佢師傅大名 <br />\n感謝師傅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885e931575344286d8976dd354451704fe8365c7","tid":2331634,"uid":56702,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"仆街女唔還錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c902347677a6a8f7fe980657e799b1b7c39955b2","tid":2331634,"uid":384505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"見到合照之後爆喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最尾個集真係勁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/p